%%% README
%%%

The radierl project implements a RADIUS protocol stack.

To build the radius application including documentation:

	$ make

To build the radius_example application:

	$ make example_callbacks

To test the radius and radius_example applications:

	$ make test

To install the radius application:

	$ ERL_TOP=/Users/otpuser/lib/erlang make install

To install the radius_example application:

	$ cd examples
	$ ERL_TOP=/Users/otpuser/lib/erlang make install

Everything here is distributed under a New BSD style license.

